Class Summary
BuyArrow BuyArrow dipicts an arrow with the point up that can be used to indicate a buy point.

GraphDailyPrices GraphDailyPrices is an implementation of GraphRedrawListener.
SellArrow SellArrow dipicts an arrow with the point down that can be used to indicate a sell point.
TestGraphManager The TestGraphManager class manages the layout of the statistical test graphs within this panel.
TestGraphPanel The TestGraphPanel creates a JPanel in which a statistical test graph can be added.
